{"tid":577361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人大代表，好撚on9，好撚虛偽","createTime":"2018-03-01T16:34:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T04:34:29.000Z","uid":28195,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e99a18f0d20d36033c52e83fa1ba572f24f423ea","tid":577361,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T16:34:32.000Z","msg":"近期的兩段片，睇睇做左幾十年人大代表既劉佩瓊，點樣為大陸既仆街野辯護<br />\n<br />\n1. 幫復闢護航，狂吹人大代表好撚勁，唔中意既話，連習帝都可以反。<br />\n但被問到為什麼大陸網絡大禁言，就話唔知道，柒到老母都唔認得。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XHZwN5upPl8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXHZwN5upPl8&d=vblYqEDm6m1M7u%2BEIZCfur%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=b3bfc6d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XHZwN5upPl8</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 幫北京清理低端人口事件護航，將他們說成90s的「盲流」，清理係好正確<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/z_q6sNo-XWA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fz_q6sNo-XWA&d=vblYqEDm6m1M7u%2BEIZCfur%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=e0fe4544\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/z_q6sNo-XWA</a>"},{"pid":"5279a61b818c24f0c548693764a53d39bc0ceccd","tid":577361,"uid":12853,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T16:47:34.000Z","msg":"琴日睇到火滾 即刻熄左 <br />\n走狗也"},{"pid":"886203c1d694f3dfc881290dea3838cffecdcec7","tid":577361,"uid":50457,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T22:38:12.000Z","msg":"呢班標準賣港狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff3bb5a01d189afaf9d43e38601b6271ddca3309","tid":577361,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T01:07:27.000Z","msg":"仲話自已好有代表性，dllm"},{"pid":"500d2d322e2ccbb344a8b89baa27c27ddd025dff","tid":577361,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T01:20:05.000Z","msg":"劉佩瓊呢d做人大好多屆，油水肯定奶唔少，都要做到咁撚樣<br />\n<br />\n新做人大果班，相信要食屎的話都會食，仲要同人講食咗好野"},{"pid":"4cf1067f368c89d0b78cd6f0fb2bea25dbe44c99","tid":577361,"uid":61675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":